    "description": "<div>Hey Team,<br><br>Creating a formal discussion task for this situation for proper tracking and recording, while following along here.<br><br>We just received emails from Google that their two locations, Caldwell and Eagle, have been suspended. <br><br>We should probably reach out to the client and notify them? <br><br><br><strong>Other Notes:</strong><br><bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiKWdpZDovL2JjMy9QZXJzb24vNDI0OTIwODA_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIghwdXIGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFQ=--b046a4ceefc2e10d49619361786996c154455d76\" content-type=\"application/vnd.basecamp.mention\"><figure>\n  <img data-avatar-for-person-id=\"42492080\" alt=\"Jason Candido\" title=\"Jason Candido, SEO at Clixsy\" class=\"avatar\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://bc3-production-assets-cdn.basecamp-static.com/4226914/people/BAhpBLBgiAI=--f02c4e5f115b3911a6b12ec9afd4e81233f4382e/avatar\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">\n  <figcaption>\n    Jason\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment> and I have not performed any work on the GBPs or touched them at all since we were granted access two days ago. <br>I am unsure whether anyone else on the SEO team did, but I don't think so, as the Dev Log would have recorded any changes made to them.<br><br>Eagle GBP suspended at 2 AM 1/16 <a href=\"https://3.basecamp.com/4226914/buckets/20058694/messages/9073677072#__recording_9475849951\">Re: GBP Changelog - DEV TEAM</a><br>Caldwell GBP suspended at 2:30 AM 1/16 <a href=\"https://3.basecamp.com/4226914/buckets/20058694/messages/9073677072#__recording_9475915388\">Re: GBP Changelog - DEV TEAM</a><br><br><bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiLmdpZDovL2JjMy9BdHRhY2htZW50LzgwNTE5NjcwMD9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiCHB1cgY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVA==--5e71c29b11750397968c56e449d981a6bd716815\" content-type=\"image/png\" url=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/bc59405e-f315-11f0-a7cf-0242ac120004/previews/full\" hre